Chinese Service Personnel Told To Learn Science And Technology
BEIJING , November 19 ( Xinhua ) -- China 's Central Military Commission ( CMC ) said that the country 's military personnel need much more training in science and technology .
The command accords with the strategic thought of President and CMC Chairman Jiang Zemin who called for " strengthening the military with science and technology " .
In these new circumstances , the CMC says , the military training needs to be increased by implementing Jiang 's strategic thought to arm the ranks and officers with technology .
The CMC has told military departments of all levels to apply the new principles to military training .
